column5: Took my neighbour to try and get him his first Lake Trout through the ice. He got A nice one, job done! We lost a few more fish and I got some whitefish. The pike were everywhere on my spot that day, got some nice ones in the mid 30‚Äùs. We have been planning to go fishing for 3 years, lol, finally made it. Jared had a nice trout supper with his family, and my crew got whitefish soup.
Have yet to step foot on any ice here Simon. Maybe this Sunday. Nice fishes by all. What were the shrimp hitting ? LOL
great photos, looks like a good time ! CHEERS
